{"word":"H6486 - פְּקֻדָּה - pᵉquddâh - pek-ood-daw' - Account","slug":"H6486","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פְּקֻדָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pᵉquddâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pek-ood-daw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Account"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E7;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - p<sup>e</sup>qu&#x0302;dda&#x0302;h</b> - <i>pek-ood-daw'</i><p/>Feminine passive participle of <a href=\"#/H6485\">H6485</a>; <i>visitation</i> (in many senses, chiefly official): - account, (that have the) charge, custody, that which . . . laid up, numbers, office (-r), ordering, oversight, + prison, reckoning, visitation."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4662\">H4662</a>, <a href=\"#/H4663\">H4663</a>, <a href=\"#/H6485\">H6485</a>, <a href=\"#/H6487\">H6487</a>, <a href=\"#/H6488\">H6488</a>, <a href=\"#/H6489\">H6489</a>, <a href=\"#/H6490\">H6490</a>, <a href=\"#/H6496\">H6496</a>"}]}